text: The Courthouse of Eidsvoll Øvre Romerike District Court (Norwegian: Øvre Romerike tingrett) is a district court located in Eidsvoll, Norway. The Court covers the area around Oslo Airport, the municipalities of Eidsvoll, Ullensaker, Nannestad, Hurdal and Nes and is subordinate to the Eidsivating Court of Appeal. == References == == External links == * Official site Category:District courts of Norway Category:Organisations based in Eidsvoll
